\name(a,r,c,p) computes a REF of {\em a} over $\ZZ/p\ZZ$.
It returns {\em ($\sigma$,r,st,d,w)}
where $\sigma$ is a permutation,
{\em r} is the number of stairs, {\em st} are the stairs,
{\em d} is the sign of $\sigma$ and {\em w} is a matrix.
